data.name: lblEarth.ToolTip
data.value: Earth Signs are "grounded" and the ones that bring us down to earth. They are mostly conservatice and realistic, but they can also be very emotional. They are connected to our material reality and can be turned into material goods. They are practical, loyal, and stable and they stick by their people through hard times.

data.name: lblHealth.Text
data.value: This week's aspect gives you a fresh burst of fiery energy to complement your already fiery nature. Look at yourself in the mirror and notice what a radiant smile you have, what an outgoing personality you have to charm people with. These are all blessings that you can be thankful for. Your greatest blessing however is good health. Are you eating plenty of healthy things each and every day? Nothing will make you feel better than a balanced diet.

data.name: lblLuck.Text
data.value: You work to create security for yourself and family and from that view point you’re driven towards acquiring assets as a means of protection. However your challenge in life would be to carve that thin balance between your desire for wealth and possessions and your own emotional peace and personal happiness.

data.name: lblTravel.Text
data.value: Work is suddenly the focus at the beginning of this week -- if you're traveling on business, connections may be difficult to make now, and if you're on a pleasure trip, thoughts of work may preoccupy you. Perhaps you have some decision to make in the career arena? Your introspection leads to great decision-making on Wednesday or Thursday, with one of those 'Aha!' moments that only happen when you're far from home. This weekend, double-check any reservations and make sure your plans are firm -- things left to chance could go away now.

data.name: lblMoney.Text
data.value: You may not be the most patient member of the Zodiac, but this week may present some issues with that way of thinking. Aspects affecting your house of relationships and home mean these areas of your life aren't exactly getting along very well. It's best to play peacemaker, even within yourself. For every concession you make to others, spend some time and money making your space more inviting.

data.name: lblCareer.Text
data.value: Your current work structure is crumbling down. The fabric is tearing apart. Let it fall. You may the one support beam that is holding everything together. It is not your responsibility to bear that much weight. Let it fall and embrace something new.

data.name: lblLove.Text
data.value: You love to let your mind wander over all the endless possibilities that the universe has to offer, and today, you will probably allow yourself to journey farther than ever. Potential love interests may not be quite sure how to take you right now. One minute you are promising them the Earth, and the next you are off in your own personal heaven.
